o</a></div></div></nav><main class=\"pt-16 min-h-screen\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center w-full\"><section class=\"relative w-full h-[90vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-4 overflow-hidden bg-black\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-40 mix-blend-overlay\" style=\"background-image:url(&quot;https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514525253344-a812da993201?q=80&amp;w=1933&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&quot;)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-transparent to-background/50\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-5xl flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6\"><span class=\"h-[2px] w-12 bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-brand font-black tracking-[0.3em] text-sm md:text-base uppercase\">107.1 FM | VALENCIA, VENEZUELA</span><span class=\"h-[2px] w-12 bg-brand\"></span></div><h1 class=\"text-6xl md:text-9xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-4 leading-none italic uppercase\">SINTONÍA <br/> <span class=\"text-brand\">TOTAL.</span></h1><h2 class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest text-white/90 mb-10 uppercase\">La número 1 del centro del país</h2><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-5\"><button class=\"px-10 py-5 bg-brand hover:bg-brand-hover text-white font-black rounded-full transition-all shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,79,0,0.4)] hover:scale-105 flex items-center gap-4 group\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"group-hover:animate-pulse\"><polygon points=\"5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3\"></polygon></svg>ESCUCHAR EN VIVO</button><a class=\"px-10 py-5 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white font-bold rounded-full border border-white/10 transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/famoso\">PUBLICIDAD</a></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-12 right-12 hidden lg:block animate-bounce\"><p class=\"text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 rotate-90 origin-right tracking-[0.5em] uppercase\">EST. 1997 - LEGADO CARLOS BRICEÑO</p></div></section><section class=\"w-full bg-brand py-6\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center gap-8 text-black\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black\">107.1</span><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">Mega Watts de Poder</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black\">+25</span><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">Años Liderando</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black\">#1</span><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">En el centro del país</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-black\">FULL</span><span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">Sintonía Total</span></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6\"><div class=\"max-w-xl\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4 tracking-tight uppercase italic\">Programación <span class=\"text-brand\">Elite.</span></h2><p class=\"text-zinc-500\">Los programas que mueven a Valencia y al centro de Venezuela. Talento, música y sintonía total todos los días.</p></div><div class=\"flex gap-2\"><div class=\"w-12 h-1 bg-brand\"></div><div class=\"w-4 h-1 bg-zinc-800\"></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 group hover:border-brand/40 transition-all duration-500 bg-zinc-900\"><span class=\"text-brand text-xs font-bold tracking-widest block mb-4\">08:00 AM - 10:00 AM</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors\">¿Qué pasó ayer?</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\">Con la conducción de <span class=\"text-white\">Alejandra Melian y Alejandro Rodríguez</span></p><div class=\"w-full h-[1px] bg-white/10 group-hover:bg-brand/30 transition-colors\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 group hover:border-brand/40 transition-all duration-500 bg-zinc-900\"><span class=\"text-brand text-xs font-bold tracking-widest block mb-4\">01:00 PM - 03:00 PM</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors\">¡Te lo dije!</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\">Con la conducción de <span class=\"text-white\">Paola Meza</span></p><div class=\"w-full h-[1px] bg-white/10 group-hover:bg-brand/30 transition-colors\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 group hover:border-brand/40 transition-all duration-500 bg-brand/10 border-brand/20\"><span class=\"text-brand text-xs font-bold tracking-widest block mb-4\">04:00 PM - 06:00 PM</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors\">Favoritas 107</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\">Con la conducción de <span class=\"text-white\">Carlos Briceño Jr.</span></p><div class=\"w-full h-[1px] bg-white/10 group-hover:bg-brand/30 transition-colors\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 group hover:border-brand/40 transition-all duration-500 bg-zinc-900\"><span class=\"text-brand text-xs font-bold tracking-widest block mb-4\">Sábados 10:00 AM</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors\">Mucha Pipol</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\">Con la conducción de <span class=\"text-white\">Eduardo Rodd y Jhonattan Parra</span></p><div class=\"w-full h-[1px] bg-white/10 group-hover:bg-brand/30 transition-colors\"></div></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-12\"><div class=\"w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-900 to-black border border-white/5 rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-10 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand/10 blur-[100px] -z-0\"></div><div class=\"z-10 flex-1\"><span class=\"text-brand font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-3 block\">Anúnciate con los líderes</span><h3 class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter uppercase italic\">Tu marca en <br/> Sintonía Total.</h3><p class=\"text-zinc-400 max-w-md text-lg leading-relaxed\">Forma parte de la emisora número 1. Llegamos a Carabobo, Aragua, Cojedes y Guárico con la mayor efectividad publicitaria.</p></div><div class=\"z-10 flex flex-col gap-4\"><a class=\"px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black font-black rounded-xl hover:bg-brand hover:text-white transition-all uppercase tracking-tighter text-sm text-center\" href=\"/famoso\">Consultar Tarifas</a><p class=\"text-[10px] text-center text-zinc-600 font-mono tracking-widest uppercase\">Publicidad 100% Efectiva</p></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/5 bg-zinc-900/20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center\"><div><img src=\"/logos-bonchona/92.png\" alt=\"Bonchona Logo\" class=\"h-16 mb-8\"/><p class=\"text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed text-sm max-w-sm\">Bonchona 107.1 FM es un legado de Carlos Briceño. Desde 1997, marcando la pauta musical y el entretenimiento en el centro de Venezuela. ¡Sintonía Total!</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-end gap-2\"><p class=\"text-zinc-700 text-8xl font-black italic select-none\">107.1</p><p class=\"text-brand font-bold tracking-[1em] text-xs uppercase -mt-4 mr-2\">Valencia</p></div></div></section></div></main><div class=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t border-white/10 z-50 flex items-center justify-between px-6 md:px-12 backdrop-blur-xl bg-opacity-95\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 w-1/3\"><div class=\"relative w-14 h-14 bg-zinc-900 rounded-xl overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center border border-white/5\"><img src=\"/logos-bonchona/92.png\" alt=\"Bonchona L